sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Service Client
    participant Keycloak as Keycloak Auth Server
    participant API as Protected API

    Client->>Client: Load client_id & client_secret
    Client->>Keycloak: POST /token (grant_type=client_credentials)
    Keycloak-->>Client: access_token (JWT)
    Client->>API: GET /resource\nAuthorization: Bearer access_token
    API->>Keycloak: Introspect/validate token
    Keycloak-->>API: Token active + claims
    API-->>Client: Protected data response
